g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過，無事</blockquote><br />\n幾時試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係今時今日架架巴士都有車cam都會捉我唔到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b07803254e5e6a7675fcea9e0c1aca91fc51b19","tid":321680,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:37:12.000Z","msg":"我都試過唔小心入左觀塘碼頭果個巴士站 即刻駛返出去 冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055a6bf7999bb4746eab4bf41c74b73f21a1ad33","tid":321680,"uid":35173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:38:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人知唔小心駛左入巴士總站有咩後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪一定會比人罰320<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGoogle左一陣都好似搵唔到人好似我咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過，無事</blockquote><br />\n幾時試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係今時今日架架巴士都有車cam都會捉我唔到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無人捉你咪無事 個個咁得閒搵返段片告你咩"},{"pid":"4cf02d35e9f39ed05db38cc0848be90159ac574e","tid":321680,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:40:38.000Z","msg":"Pol 570 code 20"},{"pid":"be45ac930d81668f2465e99663c41a19d9876c51","tid":321680,"uid":79410,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:47:31.000Z","msg":"成日都見有車入巴士站架啦.<br />\n有次我返到總站,前面架巴士未夠鐘私牌楂走.<br />\n有架的士晌我前面入左坑, 我即刻隊住佢唔俾佢出.<br />\n個的士佬等左差唔多20分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4669a43df4a29a6a1b3623503ec68d33207f8feb","tid":321680,"uid":14378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:52:29.000Z","msg":"有無停車呀？<br />\n無停話入錯咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：無車"},{"pid":"670f25d29344f8554c649c7885960b18a7c7c527","tid":321680,"uid":62915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日都見有車入巴士站架啦.<br />\n有次我返到總站,前面架巴士未夠鐘私牌楂走.<br />\n有架的士晌我前面入左坑, 我即刻隊住佢唔俾佢出.<br />\n個的士佬等左差唔多20分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打揸巴士嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"b05b630e681d2bc71d2ccea44458878c90522643","tid":321680,"uid":62915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:13:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pol 570 code 20</blockquote><br />\nGoogle左，但我冇停車係咪姐係無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e2def47424ed45e4ca965a133f901a2cb79598","tid":321680,"uid":33039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:15:00.000Z","msg":"入錯過 有警察。即抄"},{"pid":"ab37d351c57cc1650b6025e87775e99736d95629","tid":321680,"uid":30644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:18:46.000Z","msg":"係尖沙咀試過，唔識路跟前車行，點知突然dup車，我過左佢先知入左巴士總站，幾架車跟我尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過頂多咪罰錢，又唔係咩大事"},{"pid":"c5e5eb6d036b3930af3accf5ee1c0ab826b4b20c","tid":321680,"uid":62915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:44:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係尖沙咀試過，唔識路跟前車行，點知突然dup車，我過左佢先知入左巴士總站，幾架車跟我尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過頂多咪罰錢，又唔係咩大事</blockquote><br />\n我都知頂多罰錢，但係都唔想咁on9咁比人罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你最後有冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"a8e36e6b1027e28e9053a5ab11e1c8445c6ac1b1","tid":321680,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:17:39.000Z","msg":"停車/上落客先罰姐<br />\n行錯點會有事<br />\n好似觀塘駕駛學院出面果個巴士總站<br />\n新牌仔行錯左入去有幾奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61ed2143dc87bfbd5f76b4617e3a758fcacf76c","tid":321680,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:14:07.000Z","msg":"試過入錯公路啲轉車站但照行<br />\n無事"},{"pid":"ef97c2395a282db51bdecb6986f749ac2a3b0d09","tid":321680,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T21:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>停車/上落客先罰姐<br />\n行錯點會有事<br />\n好似觀塘駕駛學院出面果個巴士總站<br />\n新牌仔行錯左入去有幾奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果有只准專利巴士駛入既牌，就算行錯都可以告不守交通標誌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e57ef41eac6dedcd66c93c7282752ba2bae760","tid":321680,"uid":52656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T00:22:46.000Z","msg":"試過新牌仔入左葵興個巴士線<br />\n不過冇人理咪冇事<br />\n我有朋友仔入左 （個果時又係p牌）<br />\n比差佬見到都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d942b1709c4ade4d5ddc5c641f035a0adba137","tid":321680,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T01:20:20.000Z","msg":"P牌時入過<br />\n<br />\n唔知係站長報警定咁啱有鐵馬經過<br />\n<br />\n閃燈趕我走就算<br />\n<br />\n利申 半夜兩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717129358b05ac7db8a55d886b06c3dffb171dc1","tid":321680,"uid":67700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:29:04.000Z","msg":"試過入錯尖沙咀碼頭巴士站 好彩有條車坑無巴士停即閃<br />\n排隊等巴士既人好似望住我好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好彩無人足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27db974ed6159428231023f12bd70cf4ece4e75","tid":321680,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:33:34.000Z","msg":"唔係停車上落客有幾可會捉呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：入錯過尖沙咀碼頭個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c8823cc666beb1d60b099f64f66d583efc8b36","t